Package: pharmsignal
Type: Package
Title: Signal detection in pharmacological data (pharmacovigilance) 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ty Stanford
Maintainer: Ty Stanford <tystan@gmail.com>
Description: Signal detection in pharmacological data (pharmacovigilance).
    Implementations of Reporting Odds Ratio (ROR), 
    Proportional Reporting Ratio (PRR), 
    Bayesian Confidence Propagation Neural Network Information Component 
    (BCPNN IC, both MCMC and normal approximation),
    observed-to-expected ratio with simple shrinkage, and 
    Sequence Symmetry Analysis (SSA).
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: MCMCpack,
    dplyr,
    foreach
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
